About
Pulse
2.0
Pulse
2.0
is
a
leading
national
technology
and
business
news
publication
located
in
Ann
Arbor,
Michigan.
We
publish
important
news
about
the
people,
products,
and
companies
shaping
the
future
of
technology
and
business.
Pulse
2.0
was
founded
by
longtime
Forbes
technology
journalist
Amit
Chowdhry
and
software
engineer
Shan
Sadiq.
